title: Hour 1 - Joey Chestnut, Athlete or Not?
itunes:title: Hour 1 - Joey Chestnut, Athlete or Not?
description:
Covino & Rich are in for Dan Patrick and are having fun with day-after 4th of July observations. Filming fireworks displays? Miley Cyrus in the same category as Lee Greenwood? Grill hijackers? Plus, Covino argues with the crew and callers about 15x champion Joey Chestnut being an athlete or not! #fsrweekends
